title: CodeBlock
description: CodeBlock component.
---

 Renders a code block with a title and a code snippet.

`meta` param syntax:
- "{n}" - highlights line n
- "{n-m}" - highlights lines n-m
- "{n m}" - highlights lines n and m
- "{n n-m}" - highlights lines n and n-m
- "{n-m n}" - highlights lines n-m and n
- "{n-m n-m}" - highlights lines n-m and n-m
- "'word' 'another word'" - only used for one-line code snippets. highlights words 'word' and 'another word'

## Examples

**Basic CodeBlock**
