**Basic CodeBlock with title param and lang**
```python {% title="CodeBlock here" %}
print("Hello, World!")
```

**CodeBlock with title and code snippet**
```dockerfile {% title="Dockerfile" meta="{7}" %}
COPY --from=datadog/serverless-init:1 /datadog-init /app/datadog-init
ADD 'https://dtdg.co/latest-java-tracer' /dd_tracer/java/dd-java-agent.jar
ENV DD_SERVICE=datadog-demo-run-java
ENV DD_ENV=datadog-demo
ENV DD_VERSION=1
ENV DD_APPSEC_ENABLED=1
CMD ["/app/datadog-init", "./mvnw", "spring-boot:run"]
```

**Code tag with title, lang, meta and code snippet params. Meta param highlighting words 'file' and 'CMS'. Good for one-line code snippets.**
{% code
   code="console.log('This could come from a file or CMS!');"
   lang="js"
   title="example.js"
   meta="'file' 'CMS'" /%}



**CodeBlock with meta param. highlighting line 2 and lines 5-9.**
```json {% meta="{2 5-9}" %}
{
    "viz": "timeseries",
    "requests": [
        {
            "style": {
                "palette": "dog_classic",
                "type": "solid",
                "width": "normal"
            }
        }
    ]
}
```

**CodeBlock with disable_copy param. disables the copy button.**
```python {% disable_copy=true %}
def main():
    print("Hello, World!")
```

**CodeBlock with wrap param. wraps the code block.**
```python {% wrap=true %}
def main():
    print("Hello, World Hello, WorldHello, WorldHello, WorldHello, WorldHello, WorldHello, WorldHello, WorldHello, WorldHello, WorldHello, WorldHello, World!")
```